metadata.name: SpaceX CRS-17
metadata.description:
A Falcon 9 SpaceX rocket launches on the 4th of May 2019 with cargo for the International Space Station.

This image captures the launch’s trajectory as well as the landing of the first stage of the rocket on the “Of Course I Still Love You” autonomous spaceport drone ship.

From the project and book “Myths of the Near Future”
